    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>潜入</strong>亚特兰蒂斯令人惊叹的深处，<strong>切换</strong>机器人并操纵水位，<strong>解开</strong>尘封已久的谜题！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387740/extras/65eda6347b9b034cba4f7e11701cb190.poster.avif?t=1771402433\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387740/extras/65eda6347b9b034cba4f7e11701cb190.webm?t=1771402433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387740/extras/65eda6347b9b034cba4f7e11701cb190.mp4?t=1771402433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >切换 !</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用强大的古代科技切换视角，解锁不同能力，并通过操纵房间内的水位来改变环境。通过互动各式各样的机器人和操纵杆，你可以控制水流，进而影响环境、敌人、谜题元素甚至是角色本身。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387740/extras/c67b02b3644b7007a752207c92c29c89.poster.avif?t=1771402433\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387740/extras/c67b02b3644b7007a752207c92c29c89.webm?t=1771402433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387740/extras/c67b02b3644b7007a752207c92c29c89.mp4?t=1771402433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解开 !</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亚特兰蒂斯布满离奇的谜团和古老的谜题。利用水流和机器人独特的技能，解开这些谜题，克服意想不到的障碍，迎接挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387740/extras/62e8f3fd32a37fa955c128dc2db69192.poster.avif?t=1771402433\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387740/extras/62e8f3fd32a37fa955c128dc2db69192.webm?t=1771402433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387740/extras/62e8f3fd32a37fa955c128dc2db69192.mp4?t=1771402433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索 !</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这座沉没的城市隐藏着许多秘密，亟待发掘，诉说着早已被遗忘的故事。你会遇到出奇友好的机器人，它们被注定了永不停歇地工作，除非有人能伸出援手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387740/extras/618be3f850b525bcc2f131ee7eec1ada.poster.avif?t=1771402433\" width=600 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387740/extras/618be3f850b525bcc2f131ee7eec1ada.webm?t=1771402433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387740/extras/618be3f850b525bcc2f131ee7eec1ada.mp4?t=1771402433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
